title: Breaking down the biggest snubs from Pete Prisco's list of the Top 100 NFL Players (Football 5/19)
description:
Lists are meant to be argued and picked apart. And that's exactly what happened on this episode of Pick Six, as Will Brinson and Bryant McFadden took a preliminary look at Pete Prisco's list of the Top 100 NFL players and needless to say, had some issues with it. Brinson and BMac evaluated Prisco's misses at quarterback (3:15), wide receiver (10:05), running back (22:00) and defense (27:00)...Pete will have a chance to defend himself on tomorrow's episode as we delve further into his Top 100.
